# Public Application Insights connection string — a client-side ingestion key
# that is expected to ship in the browser bundle (NOT a secret). It is injected at
# build time by Vite. In CI it comes from the repo VARIABLE
# `VITE_APPINSIGHTS_CONNECTION_STRING`; for local builds, copy this file to `.env`
# and paste your value. When empty/absent, analytics is a safe no-op.
VITE_APPINSIGHTS_CONNECTION_STRING=
